  "description": "A wide-angle view captures a vibrant landscape featuring a dense foreground of evergreen shrubbery and trees, leading to a sprawling urban and natural panorama. The foreground is dominated by lush, textured foliage in varying shades of green. Beyond this, a cityscape is visible, nestled along the edge of a large body of water, possibly a bay or sea.  Buildings of different heights create a distinct skyline. In the distance, rolling hills and mountains form a hazy backdrop. The sky is a clear, bright blue. The lighting suggests a sunny day, casting soft shadows across the landscape. The overall composition evokes a sense of spaciousness and the interplay between natural and urban environments.",
